{"tid":672150,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"餐牌冇寫有辣，我叫間野退錢得唔得？","createTime":"2018-05-20T17:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T21:30:15.000Z","uid":22898,"like":13,"dislike":229,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"9b809a7a7509d7cf055d0d1ae4d43f80e239c2e8","tid":672150,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:21:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，頭先係甜品店，有對男女就分別叫左2碗麵。<br />\n食左一陣，個男人叫左個侍應過黎同佢講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「你碗麵好辣，但係佢menu 冇寫有辣我食唔到，可唔可以退錢？」<br />\n<br />\n咁個侍應都入廚房問，問完出黎同佢講話退唔到，又話其實英文名有寫spicy ，之後個男人即刻起鋼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「哦！姐係下下要人同你地中英對照咁睇係咪呀，我睇中文點知你係辣，辣椒圖都冇個係隔離！」<br />\n<br />\n個侍應真係唔話得，話幫佢換過碗，又話幫佢換清湯，最後補差價換左個甜品比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我走既時候，打開本menu一睇，佢個麵寫住「韓式xxxx麵」<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"5a832d177bd0809067ec6cb7345eb3ff9bd5c2cf","tid":672150,"uid":39608,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"xxxx係咩？<br />\n可能有d料正常人會預係辣"},{"pid":"121f559e719418e0bc7b9367f09b855f391bd03e","tid":672150,"uid":22898,"like":1,"dislike":102,"score":-101,"quote":{"pid":"5a832d177bd0809067ec6cb7345eb3ff9bd5c2cf","tid":672150,"uid":39608,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"xxxx係咩？<br />\n可能有d料正常人會預係辣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:25:04.000Z","msg":"Xxx好似係年糕個類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔記得，sorr<br />\n<br />\n不過我記得啲配料名的確好似唔辣"},{"pid":"2f92440bd3cac0406e9b13bfe04e9e02c91ca7d4","tid":672150,"uid":56758,"like":115,"dislike":1,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:27:37.000Z","msg":"我諗要睇埋xxxx係乜<br />\n同個樣野普遍認知係咩<br />\n正如你唔會預菠蘿包入面真係有菠蘿一樣"},{"pid":"5f0c2c980fda8e832863dfbfb9df08f71efde20a","tid":672150,"uid":22898,"like":1,"dislike":58,"score":-57,"quote":{"pid":"5a832d177bd080